snippet: Six people were killed on Sunday in clashes between groups backing rival candidates in Turkey's municipal elections, which turned into a referendum on the rule of Prime Minister Tayyip Erdogan....

headline.print_headline: Six Killed in Clashes During Municipal Elections in Turkey
headline.main: Six Killed in Clashes During Municipal Elections in Turkey

lead_paragraph: Six people were killed on Sunday in clashes between groups backing rival candidates in Turkey's municipal elections, which turned into a referendum on the rule of Prime Minister Tayyip Erdogan.
